{"type":null,"faqId":38508,"title":"天气","answer":"<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n</style>\n<div>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">天气应用不仅方便您查看当前位置的天气信息，还可查看世界各地当天以及未来几天的天气信息。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">1.</span><a name=\"_task_add_city_weather-chtext\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">添加城市</span></a>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">将关心的城市添加到天气界面，可以方便及时查看这些城市的天气信息。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在主屏幕，点击“实用工具 &gt; 天气”。</span></span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125516\" style=\"width:0.22916667in;height:0.16319445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \"> &gt; </span></span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125517\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">”，输入要添加的城市名称，搜索栏下方会列出相匹配的城市列表。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击要添加的城市。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">2.</span><a name=\"_task_check_city_weather-chtext\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">查看天气</span></a>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在主屏幕，点击“实用工具 &gt; 天气”。</span></span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">左右滑动屏幕，切换到要查看的城市，查看当地天气情况。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125518\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">”，查看更多天气指标。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">3.</span><a name=\"_task_delete_city_weather-chtext\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">删除城市</span></a>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在主屏幕，点击“实用工具 &gt; 天气”。</span></span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125519\" style=\"width:0.22916667in;height:0.16319445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">”，长按要删除的城市，然后点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125520\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">”。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125521\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">”。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">4.</span><a name=\"_task_refresh_weather-chtext\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">更新天气</span></a>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在主屏幕，点击“实用工具 &gt; 天气”。</span></span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">左右滑动屏幕，切换到要更新天气的城市。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">向下滑动屏幕，手动更新天气。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125522\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 10.5pt; \">您可以将天气设置为自动更新模式。点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125523\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); width: 0.22916667in; height: 0.16319445in; vertical-align: text-bottom; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">&gt;</span><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">&nbsp;</span></span></span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125524\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); width: 0.22777778in; height: 0.16666667in; vertical-align: text-bottom; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 10.5pt; \">”，打开“自动更新”开关，设置“更新间隔”，手机将按照设定的时间间隔定期刷新天气。</span>\n</span><br>\n</p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":1094,"faqType":"生活助手","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"z